- Structured per-tenant logging (OTW)
Inject tenant_id into every log entry via a logging context — makes log filtering trivial

- In-app notifications
Bell icon with unread count — deal assigned, stage changed, customer created by teammate

- User invite flow
Owner sends invite link → recipient creates account within the same tenant

- CSV export
Streamed export of filtered customers and deals — useful for reporting and data handoff

- Rate limiting per tenant
Throttle API requests by tenant_id, not just IP — prevents one tenant hammering the system

- Custom field key sanitisation
Reject keys with dots, dollar signs, or spaces — prevents JSONB operator injection

- Service layer test suite
PHPUnit feature tests for CustomerService, DealService, ActivityService with tenant isolation assertions

- Health check endpoint
GET /api/health — checks DB connectivity, returns 200/503 for uptime monitors

- Filter state in URL
Sync search/filter/page to query params — makes filtered views shareable and bookmarkable

- Empty state components
Friendly zero-data views with a call to action instead of a blank table

- Global error boundary
Catch unhandled Vue errors and show a friendly fallback instead of a white screen

- Route loading indicator
NProgress bar on route transitions — currently pages swap instantly with no feedback